"       John G Bartlett, MD",
"      </a>",
"     </td>",
"     <td>",
"      <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials patTopicContributorsType\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/57/14225/contributors\">",
"       Deputy Editor",
